{"tid":2367395,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳日君89歲生日 嘆周遭環境令佢沮喪","createTime":"2021-01-15T10:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T10:03:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1b629640f1c11344f90fb66015acce7701b23175","tid":2367395,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bohvRJlXSVBe99k39zRfJBbEq8Y=/802x437/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4R4J7ULITZGSPEHQWTKZOERSSQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbohvRJlXSVBe99k39zRfJBbEq8Y%3D%2F802x437%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4R4J7ULITZGSPEHQWTKZOERSSQ.png&h=4f06aafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間飛快，陳日君之後升咗樞機，退埋主教職都超過10年，但香港人仍然成日見到佢，反校本條例絕食、遊行集會爭民主、為中國教會一次又一次往返羅馬、頻繁到訪監獄，唔經唔覺早兩日係佢89歲生日，有教友特別喺《天主教信友平台》撰寫佢嘅軼事，作為送畀佢嘅生日禮物。<br />\n<br />\n文章提到嘅蝦碌嘢包括佢因為miss咗巴士，強撐上山去大嶼山塘福懲教所探監，之後腰背痛到要入醫院；得得戚show off切火腿技巧切埋自己忽手指肉；仲要為堅持己見解話：「我未夠老，要到90歲才會聽話。」仲有口出狂言話90歲要再行「最後的最後的最後一次」獅子山。<br />\n<br />\n陳日君由上海嚟香港，放下身段燒盡樞機光環，呢20年嚟堅持為受壓迫嘅香港人同中國教會發聲，受盡包括自己兄弟在內嘅人攻擊，周遭環境令佢沮喪，佢無強行正能量去掩飾，黎智英最近無法保釋，佢亦抱不平徹夜難眠，寫blog傾偈好多次提到聖詠44章「主啊！醒來吧！你為何仍舊沉睡？轉面不顧我們的痛苦和辛酸？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/MAUQQMKBNZBHZLHGDSVHTMOW3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FMAUQQMKBNZBHZLHGDSVHTMOW3Q%2F&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFl%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=016533da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210115%2FMAUQQMKBNZBHZLHGDSVHTMOW3Q%2F&h=3851f347\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210115/MAUQQMKBNZBHZLHGDSVHTMOW3Q/</a>"}]}